# problem-specific runtime parameters
# The following parameters are following Section 6.12 of D.A. Hubber et al., 2018, MNRAS 473, 1603–1632.
SinkParTest_R0                           3.0856776e+16  # The radius of the spherical cloud (in cm) [3.0e16]
SinkParTest_Omega0                       1.6e-12        # Angular velocity of the cloud (in s^-1) [0.0]
SinkParTest_Core_Mass                    1.0            # The mass of the cloud (in M_sun) [1.0]
SinkParTest_Delta_Dens                   0.5            # m=2 density perturbation [0.1]
SinkParTest_Dens_Contrast                100            # Density contrast outside R0 [100]
SinkParTest_B0                           0.0            # B field strenght (in G) [0.0]
SinkParTest_theta_B                      0.0            # Angle between B and z-axis (in degree) [0.0]
SinkParTest_Mach_num                     0.0            # Mach number for turbulence [0.0]
SinkParTest_Iso_Temp                     10.0           # The isothermal temperature (in K) for the barotropic EOS [10.0]
SinkParTest_rho_AD                       1e-14          # Transition density for Barotropic EOS (in g/cm^-3) [1e-14]
SinkParTest_Tur_Table                    Tur_Table.dat  # The turbulence table